tique software shops iflex and profitlogic will move oracle into retail and banking for now expanded oracle looking stronger sales up  this year but socalled project fusion blending oracles database technology with peoplesofts business wares not expected until  chicago native cofounded database software firm in  took public in  a day before microsoft maintained rabid rivalry ever since also competitive on the high seas bmw oracle racing team aiming to win americas cup in  recently purchased a dozen residential and commercial properties in malibu calif might have to rethink furnishing plans in light of pending  million charitable gift on behalf of oracle to settle insider trading suit distribution of the forbes  by us statediameter of disc reflects size of fortune the red disc indicates lawrence joseph ellison see distribution of forbes  since   previous next  sort list by rank  name  net worth  age  residence a d v e r t i s e m e n t richest rides the superrich and supercars gohandinhand learn what they know  hot list  sports car   recommended models reviews pricing and photos on  sports cars on forbesautoscom retractable belt barrier stanchions retractablebelt barrier stanchionswall mounted barriersstanchion posts for ropeshanging ropes plastic stanchions and chainsstorage carts for stanchionspost top sign holdersportable sign standsprinted sign insertssteel barricadesplastic barricadesexpanding length barricadesjersey and road barriersevent fence panelssportpanel pvc fencingnew portable safety zonenew retractacade barrierbellman cartsbarrier replacement partscustom printing and branding your cart is empty shipping coststimes  returns payment options standard shipments are by ups ground or truck depending on total weight  to schedule an overnight or nd day air shipment please contact us tollfree at  to place your order      easy and secure online ordering retractablebelt barrier stanchions when purchasing retractablebelt barriers dont be fooled by other website