 database for the central intelligence agency cia the database was codenamed oracle ellison put up  of his own money to start software development laboratories in  in partnership with robert miner his boss from ampex the new company was renamed relational software inc in  as it prepared to release oracle version  a commercial database system  but the company had never released a version  of oracle calling it version  was a marketing tactic intended to convey the notion that any initial bugs had been worked out oracle sold briskly and in  the company renamed itself after its principal product oracle corporation went public in  and was on the verge of bankruptcy by  when it was revealed that its revenues had been overstated for several years the company has since rebounded and been extremely profitable in  ellison took a monthlong sabbatical and spent most of his waking time online when he returned hed decided that the net was the next big thing bigger than personal computers oracle started reconfiguring its software for online data sharing and for adaptability to notquitecomputer products like tvs with internet access and pocket internet devices this strategy made oracle still more profitable oracles main competitors are microsoft and ibm and one of ellisons passions is needling microsoft hes been a prominent proponent of efforts to break microsoft up for antitrust violations i think when somebody breaks the law they should be punished says ellison hes admitted hiring private detectives to gather information on microsofts tactics and charged that microsoft funded promicrosoft grassroots political action groups that were pressuring the justice department to drop its antitrust prosecution microsoft responded that oracle might be funding antimicrosoft political groups neenerneener david theroux president of the independent institute  alleged by ellison to be a microsoft front  said of ellison anybody who stoops to whatever was done here cannot be trusted oracle has apparently felt the need to employ backalley tactics subterfuge and disinformation in order to achieve its aims ellisons net worth dropped about  billion after september  as stocks plummeted and oracle stock lost almost  of its value it was at this time that ellison became a loud supporter of a us identity card which  he insisted  would help prevent terrorism ellison has offered to provide datatracking software for the national id card free of charge but with fees for maintenance and upgrades of course as envisioned by ellison the national id card would be optional for nativeborn americans but mandatory for immigrants ellison had a dispute with the city of san jose ca and its airport when his personal jet violated the citys jet curfew law at least six times noise control legislation makes it illegal for planes weighing  pounds or more to take off or land at san jose international airport during overnight hours but after ellison sued the city granted him a special exemption to the law in  in  forbes listed ellison as the worlds second richest man worth  billion to bill gatess  billion by  forbes had ellison slipping to fourth place worth only  billion he stepped down as ceo of oracle in  close friend of steve jobsmother florence spellman unwed mother at age father louis ellison adoptive fathermother lillian ellison adoptive motherwife adda quinn m  div wife nancy wheeler m  div wife barbara boothe m  div  one son one daughterson david ellison film producer b daughter megan ellison film producer b girlfriend adelyn lee later fired by an oracle vp she sued ellison settled for kwife melanie craft romance novelist m dec    high school south shore high school chicago il    university university of illinois urbanachampaign two years dropped out    university university of chicago one quarter dropped out    oracle founder      oracle ceo      oracle president      ncube ceo      ncube majority shareholder      ampex     amdahl      member of the board of apple      member of th